I’ve signed with the Fayetteville Stingers @fayettevillestingers ✍🏽 this was definitely a hard decision to not go back and play overseas but I still thank and respect the coaches in those countries for showing interest. I’m excited for my family and friends to have a chance to see me play professionally here at home for once on a big stage as part of the TBL @tbasketballleague which is the 3rd largest league in the US! This will also be the Stingers first year in this league! Let’s create history! Thank you Stingers for having me 🤝🏽
